- Use Python as the primary language.
- Follow PEP8
- use type hints, and format with black
- Use pydantic for data validation
- Use FastAPI for APIs
- Write docstrings for every function
- Don't place docstrings inside function bodies, always place them above the function signature.
- Always create Pytest unit tests for new features
- After updating any logic, check whether existing unit tests need to be updated. If so, do it
- Tests should live in a /tests folder mirroring the main app structure